<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 06:09:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着双方进入交换协议的第四天，即最后一天，哈马斯寻求延长加沙停火时间；迄今已有 39 名以色列人获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-live/hamas-seeks-longer-cease-fire-as-sides-enter-final-day-of-swap-39-israelis-freed-so-far/0000018c-0ef1-d679-abdc-9ef9589f0000</link><description>在以色列与哈马斯协议的第三阶段，包括 9 名儿童在内的 14 名以色列人和 3 名泰国国民抵达以色列 ■ 以色列释放了 39 名巴勒斯坦安全囚犯 ■ 84 岁的以色列释放人质，在医院中生命垂危 ■ 哈马斯寻求延长停火时间 ■ 拜登表示，美国计划将战斗暂停时间延长至周一之后 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙仍有 200 多名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙有 14,854 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article-live/hamas-seeks-longer-cease-fire-as-sides-enter-final-day-of-swap-39-israelis-freed-so-far/0000018c-0ef1-d679-abdc-9ef9589f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队计划在停火结束后恢复对哈马斯的加沙进攻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-plans-to-resume-offense-on-hamas-in-gaza-once-cease-fire-ends/0000018c-0d1b-d65f-a7dd-fddfd93a0000</link><description>以色列国防军决定最终也在加沙南部开始行动，那里的哈马斯状况要好得多。以色列希望停火让哈马斯有机会看到加沙北部的破坏，这将减少他们继续战斗的动力</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-plans-to-resume-offense-on-hamas-in-gaza-once-cease-fire-ends/0000018c-0d1b-d65f-a7dd-fddfd93a0000</guid></item><item><title>在相互压力下，以色列向哈马斯发出信号，如果更多人质获释，则不急于恢复加沙战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-signals-to-hamas-no-rush-to-resume-gaza-fighting-if-more-hostages-freed/0000018c-0d75-ddff-a3bc-bdf5e82f0000</link><description>哈马斯对延长停火协议非常感兴趣，该组织告诉卡塔尔人，它将尝试寻找更多符合协议首要标准的以色列人，其中包括约 90 人。以色列国防军也需要时间来更新其部队并为下一阶段做好准备</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 04:27:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-signals-to-hamas-no-rush-to-resume-gaza-fighting-if-more-hostages-freed/0000018c-0d75-ddff-a3bc-bdf5e82f0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-27/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-0eaa-d2ae-afcf-3ffacb480000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 02:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-27/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-0eaa-d2ae-afcf-3ffacb480000</guid></item><item><title>是时候废除以色列政府冗余且成本高昂的政府部门了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-27/ty-article/time-to-scrap-the-israeli-governments-countless-redundant-ministries/0000018c-0d5a-ddff-a3bc-bdfebaae0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 00:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-27/ty-article/time-to-scrap-the-israeli-governments-countless-redundant-ministries/0000018c-0d5a-ddff-a3bc-bdfebaae0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列德鲁兹公民的特别法律？不，谢谢</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/a-special-law-for-israels-druze-citizens-no-thanks/0000018c-0cfb-d65f-a7dd-fcff89a40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 23:08:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/a-special-law-for-israels-druze-citizens-no-thanks/0000018c-0cfb-d65f-a7dd-fcff89a40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列试图阻止巴勒斯坦囚犯获释的庆祝活动揭示了战争的真正目的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-bid-to-stop-celebration-of-prisoners-release-reveals-real-aim-of-war/0000018c-0cfb-d2ae-afcf-3dfb8abb0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 22:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-bid-to-stop-celebration-of-prisoners-release-reveals-real-aim-of-war/0000018c-0cfb-d2ae-afcf-3dfb8abb0000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列人来说，哈马斯人质的释放是每晚必要的心理折磨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-hamas-hostage-releases-are-a-necessary-nightly-psychological-torture/0000018c-0cae-ddff-a3bc-bcee1a990000</link><description>哈马斯领导人伊赫·辛瓦尔不想将犹太婴儿和母亲劫持为人质。他想杀了他们。但以色列人仍然对哈马斯从家园中夺走的俘虏感到集体内疚</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 21:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-hamas-hostage-releases-are-a-necessary-nightly-psychological-torture/0000018c-0cae-ddff-a3bc-bcee1a990000</guid></item><item><title>对于拜登来说，释放四岁人质阿维盖尔始终是个人的事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/for-biden-freeing-four-year-old-hostage-avigail-mor-idan-was-always-personal/0000018c-0d63-d2ae-afcf-3df305820000</link><description>一位美国政府高级官员表示，自危机爆发以来，拜登总统一直关注美国人质问题，并补充说，“我们无法确认十名人质中许多人的下落或状况”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 21:20:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/for-biden-freeing-four-year-old-hostage-avigail-mor-idan-was-always-personal/0000018c-0d63-d2ae-afcf-3df305820000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列和加沙战争引发的伊斯兰恐惧症加剧，三名巴勒斯坦学生在佛蒙特州伯灵顿遭到枪击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinian-students-shot-in-burlington-vermont-amid-spiking-islamphobia/0000018c-0d4e-ddff-a3bc-bdeeb2e40000</link><description>伯灵顿警察局长乔恩·穆拉德 (Jon Murad) 表示：“在这个紧张的时刻，任何人在看到这起事件时都会怀疑这可能是一起出于仇恨动机的犯罪。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 20:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinian-students-shot-in-burlington-vermont-amid-spiking-islamphobia/0000018c-0d4e-ddff-a3bc-bdeeb2e40000</guid></item><item><title>美国希望以色列和哈马斯四天的暂停能够延长至周一之后，以确保更多人质安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-hopes-israel-hamas-four-day-pause-can-be-extended-past-monday-to-secure-more-hostages/0000018c-0d34-d2ae-afcf-3df67c510000</link><description>国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文表示，以色列“准备好继续暂停战斗，哈马斯每天都会额外释放 10 名人质”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 20:28:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-hopes-israel-hamas-four-day-pause-can-be-extended-past-monday-to-secure-more-hostages/0000018c-0d34-d2ae-afcf-3df67c510000</guid></item><item><title>别再为哈马斯的“人性”鼓掌了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-26/ty-article/.highlight/stop-applauding-hamas-for-its-humanity/0000018c-0d33-ddff-a3bc-bdf7cc6a0000</link><description>我们必须承认，哈马斯枪手在杀害其家人（有时是在他们眼前）后在镜头前与俘虏击掌，这为人性设置了很低的门槛</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 20:15:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-26/ty-article/.highlight/stop-applauding-hamas-for-its-humanity/0000018c-0d33-ddff-a3bc-bdf7cc6a0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯周六释放 39 名巴勒斯坦囚犯，其中 8 人被判谋杀未遂罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/8-of-the-39-palestinian-prisoners-released-in-hamas-deal-convicted-of-attempted-murder/0000018c-0ce4-d2ae-afcf-3df66a2a0000</link><description>作为从以色列监狱释放 39 名巴勒斯坦妇女和儿童的交换条件，哈马斯从加沙释放了 13 名被囚禁的以色列妇女和儿童</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 19:23:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/8-of-the-39-palestinian-prisoners-released-in-hamas-deal-convicted-of-attempted-murder/0000018c-0ce4-d2ae-afcf-3df66a2a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部基布兹居民阻止巴勒斯坦人收获橄榄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/northern-israeli-kibbutz-residents-prevent-palestinians-from-harvesting-their-olives/0000018c-0cc4-ddff-a3bc-bce4f31b0000</link><description>多年来，巴勒斯坦人一直被允许通过边境收获橄榄。今年，附近基布兹的居民举行抗议活动，阻止他们这样做。尽管最初授予巴勒斯坦人进入权，但以色列军队拒绝驱散抗议者</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 18:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/northern-israeli-kibbutz-residents-prevent-palestinians-from-harvesting-their-olives/0000018c-0cc4-ddff-a3bc-bce4f31b0000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚称以色列袭击导致大马士革机场停止服务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strike-puts-damascus-airport-out-of-service/0000018c-0ca4-d679-abdc-9ebcc0db0000</link><description>据报道，以色列多年来一直对其所谓的叙利亚境内与伊朗有关的目标进行袭击，而美国最近也证实，以色列针对叙利亚境内的伊斯兰革命卫队设施进行了袭击，以回应针对美国人员的袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 18:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strike-puts-damascus-airport-out-of-service/0000018c-0ca4-d679-abdc-9ebcc0db0000</guid></item><item><title>人权观察称阿赫利医院爆炸可能由巴勒斯坦火箭造成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/al-ahli-hospital-explosion-likely-caused-by-palestinian-rocket-human-rights-watch-says/0000018c-0c96-d65f-a7dd-fcd7c1cc0000</link><description>该事件的最初报道引用了哈马斯的说法，即以色列轰炸了该医院，并在爆炸中造成 500 人死亡——人权观察现在表示这两种说法不太可能是正确的</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 17:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/al-ahli-hospital-explosion-likely-caused-by-palestinian-rocket-human-rights-watch-says/0000018c-0c96-d65f-a7dd-fcd7c1cc0000</guid></item><item><title>油轮在也门海岸被劫持，这是自加沙战争开始以来第三次针对与以色列有关的船只的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/israeli-linked-tanker-hijacked-off-coast-of-yemen/0000018c-0be4-d679-abdc-9ffc65b10000</link><description>不到一周前，也门胡塞叛军劫持了一艘货船，该货船部分归以色列商人旗下的一家公司所有。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 16:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/israeli-linked-tanker-hijacked-off-coast-of-yemen/0000018c-0be4-d679-abdc-9ffc65b10000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，全女性以色列坦克兵在 17 个小时的战斗中杀死了 50 名恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/all-woman-israeli-tank-crews-killed-50-terrorists-over-17-hours-of-combat-on-october-7/0000018c-0bec-d65f-a7dd-fbfff6dd0000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，这些坦克乘员由20岁出头的年轻女性组成，是第一批投入战斗的西方女装甲兵。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 15:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/all-woman-israeli-tank-crews-killed-50-terrorists-over-17-hours-of-combat-on-october-7/0000018c-0bec-d65f-a7dd-fbfff6dd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人遭到屠杀和绑架？阿拉伯媒体上没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-massacred-and-abducted-not-in-the-arab-media/0000018c-0b89-de3d-af9e-0bdfaf9c0000</link><description>相反，哈马斯的袭击在很大程度上被描述为合法的抵抗行为，尽管并非每个国家的媒体都将加沙的恐怖组织与巴勒斯坦人民等同起来</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 14:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-massacred-and-abducted-not-in-the-arab-media/0000018c-0b89-de3d-af9e-0bdfaf9c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国大学校园的哈马斯与以色列辩论并未以毒性为主导</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/progressive-trolls-dont-rule-the-israel-hamas-war-debate-on-u-s-campuses/0000018c-0b5d-dca2-a9fd-6fdf526f0000</link><description>作为在美国大学工作的犹太裔以色列学者，我们知道校园中两极分化和背叛的形象被夸大了。我们遇到的大多数学生和同事都充满好奇和开放的态度，想了解更多有关以色列-哈马斯战争的信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 13:31:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/progressive-trolls-dont-rule-the-israel-hamas-war-debate-on-u-s-campuses/0000018c-0b5d-dca2-a9fd-6fdf526f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>